---
import '../styles/global.css';
---

<html lang="fr" class="scroll-smooth">
  <head>
    <meta charset="utf-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1" />
    <title>DevForge - La Forge Logicielle Autonome</title>
    <meta name="description" content="Déployez vos applications avec 14 agents IA spécialisés." />
  </head>
  <body class="bg-slate-950 text-white selection:bg-blue-500/30 font-sans antialiased">
    <div class="drawer drawer-end">
      <input id="landing-drawer" type="checkbox" class="drawer-toggle" />
      <div class="drawer-content flex flex-col">
        <!-- Navbar -->
        <nav class="sticky top-0 z-50 w-full border-b border-white/10 bg-slate-950/80 backdrop-blur-md">
          <div class="mx-auto flex max-w-7xl items-center justify-between px-6 py-4">
            <div class="flex items-center gap-2">
              <div class="h-8 w-8 rounded bg-gradient-to-br from-blue-500 to-indigo-600 flex items-center justify-center font-bold text-lg">F</div>
              <span class="text-xl font-bold tracking-tight text-white">DevForge</span>
            </div>
            <div class="hidden md:flex gap-8 text-sm font-medium text-slate-300">
              <a href="#features" class="hover:text-white transition">Fonctionnalités</a>
              <a href="#agents" class="hover:text-white transition">L'Équipe</a>
              <a href="#pricing" class="hover:text-white transition">Tarifs</a>
            </div>
            <div class="hidden md:flex items-center gap-4">
              <a href="/login" class="text-sm font-medium text-slate-300 hover:text-white transition">Connexion</a>
              <a href="/apps" class="rounded-lg bg-blue-600 px-4 py-2 text-sm font-semibold text-white hover:bg-blue-500 transition shadow-[0_0_15px_rgba(37,99,235,0.4)]">
                Accéder au Dashboard
              </a>
            </div>
            <label for="landing-drawer" class="btn btn-ghost btn-square btn-sm md:hidden">
              <svg class="w-6 h-6" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M4 6h16M4 12h16M4 18h16" />
              </svg>
            </label>
          </div>
        </nav>

        <!-- Hero Section -->
        <main>
      <section class="relative overflow-hidden pt-32 pb-20 lg:pt-48 lg:pb-32">
        <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-[url('https://grainy-gradients.vercel.app/noise.svg')] opacity-20 mix-blend-overlay pointer-events-none"></div>
        <div class="absolute -top-24 -left-24 h-96 w-96 rounded-full bg-blue-600/20 blur-[120px] pointer-events-none"></div>
        <div class="absolute top-1/2 right-0 h-96 w-96 -translate-y-1/2 rounded-full bg-indigo-600/20 blur-[120px] pointer-events-none"></div>

        <div class="relative mx-auto max-w-7xl px-6 text-center">
          <div class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 rounded-full border border-blue-500/30 bg-blue-500/10 px-3 py-1 mb-8">
            <span class="flex h-2 w-2 rounded-full bg-blue-500 animate-pulse"></span>
            <span class="text-xs font-medium text-blue-300">OpenClaw + Ollama (qwen2.5:32b) propulsé</span>
          </div>
          
          <h1 class="mx-auto max-w-4xl text-5xl font-extrabold tracking-tight text-white sm:text-7xl">
            L'usine logicielle <span class="text-transparent bg-clip-text bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-400 to-indigo-500">entièrement autonome</span>
          </h1>
          
          <p class="mx-auto mt-6 max-w-2xl text-lg text-slate-300">
            De l'idée au déploiement en production. Pilotez 14 agents IA spécialisés pour créer, tester, et héberger vos applications sur votre propre infrastructure.
          </p>
          
          <div class="mt-10 flex flex-wrap items-center justify-center gap-4">
            <a href="/apps" class="rounded-lg bg-white px-8 py-3.5 text-sm font-semibold text-slate-900 hover:bg-slate-100 transition shadow-lg">
              Démarrer un projet
            </a>
            <a href="#demo" class="rounded-lg bg-slate-800 border border-slate-700 px-8 py-3.5 text-sm font-semibold text-white hover:bg-slate-700 transition">
              Voir la Démo
            </a>
          </div>
          
          <!-- Dashboard Preview Image/Mockup -->
          <div class="mt-20 mx-auto max-w-5xl rounded-2xl border border-white/10 bg-slate-900/50 p-2 backdrop-blur-sm shadow-2xl">
            <div class="rounded-xl overflow-hidden bg-slate-950 border border-slate-800/50 relative">
               <div class="absolute top-0 w-full h-8 bg-slate-900 border-b border-slate-800 flex items-center px-4 gap-2">
                 <div class="w-3 h-3 rounded-full bg-red-500/80"></div>
                 <div class="w-3 h-3 rounded-full bg-yellow-500/80"></div>
                 <div class="w-3 h-3 rounded-full bg-green-500/80"></div>
               </div>
               <div class="pt-8 p-6 text-left font-mono text-sm text-blue-400">
                 <p><span class="text-green-400">~/forge</span> $ openclaw task "CREATE_NEW_APP saas-billing"</p>
                 <p class="text-slate-400 mt-2">[CHEF_TECHNIQUE] Ordre reçu. Initialisation du dépôt GitHub...</p>
                 <p class="text-slate-400">[ARCHITECTE_LOGICIEL] Génération de l'architecture Astro + Tailwind...</p>
                 <p class="text-slate-400">[DEV_BACKEND] Création de l'API Stripe en cours...</p>
                 <p class="text-emerald-400 mt-2">✓ Application générée avec succès ! Déploiement Docker en préparation.</p>
               </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <!-- Features Section -->
      <section id="features" class="py-24 bg-slate-900/50 border-y border-white/5">
        <div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl px-6">
          <div class="text-center max-w-2xl mx-auto mb-16">
            <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold tracking-tight text-white sm:text-4xl">Conçu pour la productivité absolue</h2>
            <p class="mt-4 text-slate-400">Notre essaim de 14 agents IA gère le cycle de vie complet de vos applications, de la première ligne de code jusqu'au monitoring en production.</p>
          </div>
          
          <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
            <div class="bg-slate-900 border border-slate-800 rounded-2xl p-8 hover:border-blue-500/50 transition duration-300">
              <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-lg bg-blue-500/20 flex items-center justify-center mb-6">
                <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-blue-400" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M10 20l4-16m4 4l4 4-4 4M6 16l-4-4 4-4" />
                </svg>
              </div>
              <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-white mb-3">Code Généré par l'IA</h3>
              <p class="text-slate-400 leading-relaxed">Les agents utilisent Qwen 2.5 (32b et 7b-coder) pour rédiger un code propre, moderne et documenté. Spécialisés Astro, React (Preact) et Node.</p>
            </div>
            
            <div class="bg-slate-900 border border-slate-800 rounded-2xl p-8 hover:border-indigo-500/50 transition duration-300">
              <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-lg bg-indigo-500/20 flex items-center justify-center mb-6">
                <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-indigo-400" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 11H5m14 0a2 2 0 012 2v6a2 2 0 01-2 2H5a2 2 0 01-2-2v-6a2 2 0 012-2m14 0V9a2 2 0 00-2-2M5 11V9a2 2 0 002-2m0 0V5a2 2 0 012-2h6a2 2 0 012 2v2M7 7h10" />
                </svg>
              </div>
              <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-white mb-3">Déploiement ZimaOS</h3>
              <p class="text-slate-400 leading-relaxed">Intégration native avec CasaOS/ZimaOS. Les agents génèrent les `docker-compose.yml` et configurent automatiquement l'infrastructure.</p>
            </div>
            
            <div class="bg-slate-900 border border-slate-800 rounded-2xl p-8 hover:border-purple-500/50 transition duration-300">
              <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-lg bg-purple-500/20 flex items-center justify-center mb-6">
                <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-purple-400" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m5.618-4.016A11.955 11.955 0 0112 2.944a11.955 11.955 0 01-8.618 3.04A12.02 12.02 0 003 9c0 5.591 3.824 10.29 9 11.622 5.176-1.332 9-6.03 9-11.622 0-1.042-.133-2.052-.382-3.016z" />
                </svg>
              </div>
              <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-white mb-3">Autonomie & Sécurité</h3>
              <p class="text-slate-400 leading-relaxed">La forge s'auto-régule. Les agents font des PR, effectuent des revues de sécurité, et maintiennent le code sans intervention humaine.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <!-- Pricing / Plans -->
      <section id="pricing" class="py-24 relative">
        <div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl px-6">
          <div class="text-center max-w-2xl mx-auto mb-16">
            <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold tracking-tight text-white sm:text-4xl">Hébergez l'intelligence</h2>
            <p class="mt-4 text-slate-400">Choisissez le plan adapté à vos besoins de production logicielle.</p>
          </div>
          
          <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 max-w-4xl mx-auto">
            <!-- Plan 1 -->
            <div class="bg-slate-900 border border-slate-800 rounded-2xl p-8 flex flex-col">
              <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-white mb-2">Self-Hosted</h3>
              <p class="text-slate-400 text-sm mb-6">Pour les NAS personnels et ZimaBoard.</p>
              <div class="text-4xl font-bold text-white mb-6">0€ <span class="text-lg font-normal text-slate-500">/mois</span></div>
              <ul class="space-y-3 mb-8 flex-1 text-slate-300 text-sm">
                <li class="flex items-center gap-2"><svg class="w-4 h-4 text-emerald-500" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/></svg> 14 Agents Locaux (Ollama)</li>
                <li class="flex items-center gap-2"><svg class="w-4 h-4 text-emerald-500" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/></svg> Déploiements illimités</li>
                <li class="flex items-center gap-2"><svg class="w-4 h-4 text-emerald-500" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/></svg> Intégration GitHub</li>
              </ul>
              <a href="/apps" class="block w-full text-center rounded-lg bg-slate-800 px-4 py-2.5 text-sm font-semibold text-white hover:bg-slate-700 transition">Commencer gratuitement</a>
            </div>
            
            <!-- Plan 2 -->
            <div class="bg-slate-800 border-2 border-blue-500 rounded-2xl p-8 flex flex-col relative overflow-hidden">
              <div class="absolute top-0 right-0 bg-blue-500 text-white text-xs font-bold px-3 py-1 rounded-bl-lg uppercase tracking-wider">Populaire</div>
              <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-white mb-2">Cloud Forge</h3>
              <p class="text-slate-400 text-sm mb-6">Pour les entreprises et freelances.</p>
              <div class="text-4xl font-bold text-white mb-6">49€ <span class="text-lg font-normal text-slate-500">/mois</span></div>
              <ul class="space-y-3 mb-8 flex-1 text-slate-300 text-sm">
                <li class="flex items-center gap-2"><svg class="w-4 h-4 text-blue-400" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/></svg> Agents propulsés par GPT-4 / Claude 3</li>
                <li class="flex items-center gap-2"><svg class="w-4 h-4 text-blue-400" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/></svg> Cluster GPU Dédié</li>
                <li class="flex items-center gap-2"><svg class="w-4 h-4 text-blue-400" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/></svg> Auto-Scaling ZimaOS</li>
                <li class="flex items-center gap-2"><svg class="w-4 h-4 text-blue-400" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/></svg> Support prioritaire Slack</li>
              </ul>
              <a href="#" class="block w-full text-center rounded-lg bg-blue-600 px-4 py-2.5 text-sm font-semibold text-white hover:bg-blue-500 transition shadow-[0_0_15px_rgba(37,99,235,0.4)]">S'abonner</a>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>
    </main>

    <!-- Footer -->
    <footer class="border-t border-white/10 py-12 bg-slate-950 mt-12">
      <div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl px-6 flex flex-col md:flex-row items-center justify-between gap-4">
        <div class="flex items-center gap-2">
          <div class="h-6 w-6 rounded bg-blue-600 flex items-center justify-center font-bold text-xs">F</div>
          <span class="text-sm font-semibold text-slate-300">DevForge Inc.</span>
        </div>
        <p class="text-slate-500 text-sm">© {new Date().getFullYear()} DevForge SaaS. Créé avec 💙 par les Agents IA.</p>
        <div class="flex gap-4 text-sm text-slate-400">
          <a href="#" class="hover:text-white transition">Conditions</a>
          <a href="#" class="hover:text-white transition">Confidentialité</a>
          <a href="#" class="hover:text-white transition">Contact</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </footer>

    <div class="drawer-side z-[60]">
      <label for="landing-drawer" aria-label="close sidebar" class="drawer-overlay"></label>
      <ul class="menu p-6 w-80 min-h-full bg-slate-900 text-white flex flex-col gap-4">
        <li class="mb-4">
           <div class="flex items-center gap-2">
             <div class="h-8 w-8 rounded bg-gradient-to-br from-blue-500 to-indigo-600 flex items-center justify-center font-bold text-lg">F</div>
             <span class="text-xl font-bold tracking-tight text-white">DevForge</span>
           </div>
        </li>
        <li><a href="#features" class="text-lg">Fonctionnalités</a></li>
        <li><a href="#agents" class="text-lg">L'Équipe</a></li>
        <li><a href="#pricing" class="text-lg">Tarifs</a></li>
        <div class="divider"></div>
        <li><a href="/login" class="text-lg">Connexion</a></li>
        <li>
          <a href="/apps" class="btn btn-primary text-white mt-4 no-underline">
            Accéder au Dashboard
          </a>
        </li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </div>
  </body>
</html>
